!
! SNMP Access Control Lists for DISA STIG V-220526
! Restricts SNMP access to authorized monitoring systems
!
ip access-list SNMP_RO_ACL
   10 remark ** Permit SNMP Read-Only from Monitoring Systems **
   10 permit ip {{ arista_monitoring_network | default('10.0.0.0/24') }} any
   9999 remark ** Deny and Log Everything Else **
   9999 deny ip any any log
!
ip access-list SNMP_RW_ACL
   10 remark ** Permit SNMP Read-Write from Management Systems **
   10 permit ip {{ arista_mgmt_network | default('10.0.0.0/24') }} any
   9999 remark ** Deny and Log Everything Else **
   9999 deny ip any any log
!
